## 4. Landing Page Patterns

AI creates landing page code directly.

### High-Conversion Structure
1. **Hero** — Headline + subline + CTA + screenshot
2. **Problem** — 3 pain points (user relates)
3. **Solution** — 3 features (benefit-focused, not feature-focused)
4. **Social Proof** — Testimonials/stats/logos
5. **Pricing** — Clear tiers (if paid)
6. **FAQ** — Top 5 objections answered
7. **Final CTA** — Repeat main CTA
8. **Footer** — Legal, social links

### CTA per Goal
| Goal | CTA |
|------|-----|
| 💰 Revenue | "Bắt đầu dùng thử miễn phí" |
| 🆓 Free | "Tải miễn phí ngay" |
| 👥 Community | "⭐ Star on GitHub" |
| 🏆 Reputation | "Xem demo" |

