## 5. Payment Setup (Localized, Updated 2026)

### 🇻🇳 Vietnam
| Provider | Type | Fee | Best For |
|----------|------|-----|----------|
| **SePay** | Bank transfer auto | Free | Indie dev, startup |
| **MoMo** | E-wallet | 1-2% | Consumer app |
| **VNPay** | Gateway | 1.5-2% | Enterprise |
| **ZaloPay** | E-wallet | 1-2% | Zalo ecosystem |
| **Stripe VN** | Card gateway | 2.9% | SaaS global |

### 🇯🇵 Japan
| Provider | Type | Fee | Best For |
|----------|------|-----|----------|
| **PayPay** | QR | 1.6-1.98% | Consumer |
| **Stripe JP** | Card | 3.6% | SaaS |
| **Konbini** | Cash | ¥130-300/tx | Users who prefer cash |
| **LINE Pay** | E-wallet | 2.45% | LINE ecosystem |

### 🇨🇳 China
| Provider | Type | Fee | Best For |
|----------|------|-----|----------|
| **WeChat Pay** | Super app | 0.6% | In-app |
| **Alipay** | E-wallet | 0.6% | Cross-border |

### 🌍 Global
| Provider | Type | Fee | Best For |
|----------|------|-----|----------|
| **Stripe** | Card gateway | 2.9%+30¢ | #1 for devs |
| **Paddle** | MoR | 5%+50¢ | Auto tax handling |
| **LemonSqueezy** | MoR | 5%+50¢ | Indie SaaS |
| **PayPal** | E-wallet | 2.9%+30¢ | US/EU users |

### Smart Default Rule
```
If target == "VN" && goal == "indie" → recommend SePay
If target == "VN" && goal == "consumer" → recommend MoMo
If target == "global" && goal == "SaaS" → recommend Stripe
If target == "global" && goal == "indie" → recommend LemonSqueezy
```

---

## 6. Launch Calendar (30-Day Template)

### Pre-Launch (Day -7 to -1)
- Day -7: Teaser post on main channel
- Day -5: Behind-the-scenes (build story)
- Day -3: Sneak peek (screenshot/video)
- Day -1: "Launching tomorrow!" hype post

### Launch Week (Day 1-7)
- Day 1: LAUNCH — post all channels simultaneously
- Day 2: Share metrics ("100 users in 24h!")
- Day 3: Thank you post
- Day 5: First user testimonial
- Day 7: Week 1 recap

### Growth Phase (Day 8-30)
- Day 10: Feature update post
- Day 14: Tutorial/how-to content
- Day 21: Community highlight
- Day 30: Month 1 milestone celebration

---

## 7. Post-Launch Retention

### Onboarding
- AI creates first-time user flow
- Welcome email template
- Quick-start guide

### Re-engagement
- Day 3: "How's it going?" email
- Day 7: "Feature you missed" notification
- Day 14: "We improved X based on feedback"

### Feedback Collection
- In-app feedback form template
- NPS survey template
- User interview questions

---

## 8. Growth Metrics Dashboard

### What to Track per Goal
| Goal | Primary Metric | Secondary |
|------|---------------|-----------|
| 💰 Revenue | MRR, ARR | Churn, LTV, CAC |
| 🆓 Free | DAU, MAU | Retention D1/D7/D30 |
| 👥 Community | Stars, contributors | PRs, issues, forks |
| 🏆 Reputation | Page views, shares | Inbound leads |

### Analytics Setup
- Recommend: Plausible (privacy-friendly) or Google Analytics
- AI creates tracking code + dashboard template
